class.description:
[JustAMCPResourceExecutor] owns registered [JustAMCPResource] instances and resolves read requests by URI. It supports both fixed resources, such as system logs, and URI templates, such as project files under [code]res://[/code].
[codeblock]
var resources = JustAMCPResourceExecutor.new()
var templates = resources.list_resource_templates()
var project_file = resources.read_resource("res://project.godot")
print(templates)
print(project_file)
[/codeblock]
